text: Jhanda may refer to: *Jhanda is a town in Swabi District of Khyber- Pakhtunkhwa. *Jhanda Bagga Nawan is a village in the Firozpur district of Punjab, India. *Jhanda (Ludhiana West) is a village in Ludhiana district of Punjab, India. *Jhanda Singh Dhillon was a famous royal Sikh warrior. *Madho Jhanda is a village in Kapurthala district of Punjab, India.
title: Jhanda (disambiguation)
